criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients followed for Crohn's disease;

          -  Crohn's disease diagnosed in accordance with the criteria of the European Crohn's and
             Colitis Organization (ECCO);

          -  Benefiting from an abdominal ultrasound as part of their usual follow-up;

          -  Not having expressed his opposition to participate in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Persons of legal age subject to legal protection (protection of justice, guardianship,
             tutorship), persons deprived of their liberty.
